calculations.name: Bins
calculations.tableau_expression:
IF [Edad graduando ] <= 19 AND [Edad graduando ] <=19
THEN "Menor de 20"

ELSEIF  [Edad graduando ] >= 20 AND [Edad graduando ] <=25
THEN "20-25"

ELSEIF 
[Edad graduando ] >= 26 AND [Edad graduando ] <=30
THEN "26-30"

ELSEIF 
[Edad graduando ] >= 31 AND [Edad graduando ] <=40
THEN "31-40"

ELSEIF 
[Edad graduando ] >= 41 AND [Edad graduando ] <=50
THEN "41-50"

ELSEIF 
[Edad graduando ] >= 51 AND [Edad graduando ] <=60
THEN "51-60"

ELSEIF 
[Edad graduando ] >= 61 AND [Edad graduando ] <=69
THEN "60-69"

END
